        String getId()
        This method gets the ID from the request parameters.
        Returns:
        the id. Will be the empty string if NOT set in request.

      • getType

        This method gets the type from the request parameters.

      • getTotalHitCount

        int getTotalHitCount()
        This method gets the total number of hits from the request parameters.
        Returns:
        the totalHitCount or -1 if NOT set in request.

      • getHitsPerPage

        int getHitsPerPage()
        This method gets the number of hits per page from the request parameters.
        Returns:
        the hitsPerPage. Will be SearchResultPage.DEFAULT_HITS_PER_PAGE if NOT set in request.

      • getPageNumber

        int getPageNumber()
        This method gets the page-index from the request parameters.
        Returns:
        the pageNumber. Will be 0 if NOT set in request.
